Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多得追加肥料了呢
